{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"9":"The Chapters on Marriage"},"section_detail":{"9":{"hadithnumber_first":1845,"hadithnumber_last":2015,"arabicnumber_first":1845,"arabicnumber_last":2015}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1884,"arabicnumber":1884,"text":"حدثنا ابو بكر بن ابي شيبة، حدثنا يحيى بن سعيد، وابو اسامة عن عبيد الله، عن ابي الزناد، عن الاعرج، عن ابي هريرة، قال نهى رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم عن الشغار","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim"}],"reference":{"book":9,"hadith":40}}]}